    "According to Eq.",
    "( 2), points falling into cell C t will be mapped to the same interval [t, t + 1), thus preserving spatial locality.",
    "After constructing the grid, all data points are projected to 1-D space using Eq.",
    "( 2) and partitioned to shards.",
    "A shard prediction function is then trained to map each point to its shard ID."
  ],
